{"tid":1601201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「10.1行動討論」嘅然過海咁易進行大搜捕，唔過海得唔得？","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T07:20:06.000Z","uid":53876,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"819b49768660cb4575b2c478329d697e79d9cb98","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"經過尋晚9.28大家都見到政府決心進行大搜捕<br />\n而過海嘅交通選項唔多<br />\n黨鐵入面晨早企哂狗<br />\n巴士係隧道口全車搜身<br />\n搭船係碼頭搜捕<br />\n基本上香港同九龍嘅交通都死<br />\n10.1集中係港島搞定九龍搞都死<br />\n一樣有人要過海<br />\n<br />\n於是我諗可唔可以分開兩邊各自搞？<br />\n<br />\n港島人留返係港島<br />\n參照返民陣路線<br />\n<br />\n九龍新界人去九龍<br />\n太子行彌敦道去尖沙咀<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係集合同散水都會安全得多"},{"pid":"661b4a2cbf991f0ca666e54015b0de86136c80b4","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"385bdcd948b3122e5854014acf46c54d64fe23f0","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ff669e99d335fe772f2483a3157c8eaf739fb1e4","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d13c5622cab05015367b2206a337db25fdf88afd","tid":1601201,"uid":5421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"所以咪話要遍地開花 85 模式"},{"pid":"54320dea5f2af6b20f843ebfc7ba5df501a11433","tid":1601201,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"策略！港島遊行易被四面包抄，希望以後大遊行改九龍舉行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1571323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1571323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a3c2ca1331a37e860470abe49c21c715a7079e3","tid":1601201,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知我有無聽錯，十月一日皇上閱兵期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">假如同一時間有遊行，係絕對唔會有清場行動。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令皇上即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。但之前上面會嚇窒唔俾大家出，但如果出咗佢都耐你唔何。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講十一閱兵期間嘅和平遊行，唔會有清場鎮壓！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585568\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈！中共極懼怕網絡信息安全在國慶節前出事！兄弟們即刻行動香港可獲勝！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574727\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「習近平下台」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d85a6bffa40d3ac8dbf4ab74027a38e21334d7c2","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d13c5622cab05015367b2206a337db25fdf88afd","tid":1601201,"uid":5421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"所以咪話要遍地開花 85 模式"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:09:36.000Z","msg":"我想提出嘅係唔好似8.5咁分散<br />\n係集中得嚟又可以免除過海個風險"},{"pid":"7294c5193362e84710debc6e6f6158d6c4552fa7","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d67e37d98bf33b09a420bca60f87c21bc3397ac8","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"ecc62d0f2c26e2a51276af4548c1628923acf846","tid":1601201,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:13:18.000Z","msg":"要去既ok 唔帶gear 返去五區開花既就"},{"pid":"e3b6971feeac8e8d3af603cf631d7dcf63b9afdb","tid":1601201,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"abe967b58c001fb390cab35d2f370a42cc9439a9","tid":160120